口集合，護送夜歸女居民<br />\n<br />\n因差佬無能！香港人要自救！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T08:02:04.000Z","msg":"人地冇組織名呀嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n條例寫名有組織/訓練/裝備 呢三樣野是但一樣都可能會中"},{"pid":"983994eab9e28482fc277ba65afc340a5391149c","tid":1361891,"uid":8948,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T08:03:13.000Z","msg":"今時今日，唔係話自我審查，我都明大家對黑警無信任，好想靠自己既力量去守護民眾，但係法律上係咁講，真係唔好亂踩界<br />\n<br />\n至少唔好擺上枱面黎搞啦大佬呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好擔心你地好似帝吧咁未出發先入冊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87b94a3f2d3aa1f65cf341da998bb85613879a9f","tid":1361891,"uid":25758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T08:06:26.000Z","msg":"公安條例香港要守？"},{"pid":"e9903d0c76a49c8c7e8f22f0ec1a21ebaedb1d6f","tid":1361891,"uid":8948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"87b94a3f2d3aa1f65cf341da998bb85613879a9f","tid":1361891,"uid":25758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T08:06:26.000Z","msg":"公安條例香港要守？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T08:11:35.000Z","msg":"咁當然你做好心理準備就冇問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但做好心理準備都要做好準備唔好俾人滲透"},{"pid":"5b505796d4dca25fadda4d514ad2ec83f4d2d63a","tid":1361891,"uid":187913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T08:38:39.000Z","msg":"開間公司，成立會員制，申請保安公司牌....."},{"pid":"55c5baf93fa97fad2b61c247b5a4c4315da8920d","tid":1361891,"uid":261478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite